text:
T-shirts are going missing! Is this an anomalous phenomenon?
Come to Inori's pop's office, and I'll fill you in!

View Mission Details {decision}

I received a mysterious message, and I'm trying to figure it out.
Come to Inori's pop's office to help me!

View Mission Details {decision}

There's information about a mysterious phenomenon in
Shinjuku Park! Let's meet up at the Waterfall Plaza in the park!

View Mission Details {decision}

I'm the only one left here now, and I'm having trouble with
something. Can you come to Abyss Beach to help?

View Mission Details {decision}

Help! Me trapped in Abyss Sanctuary prison! Me hope
somebody gets this!

View Mission Details {decision}

Ouch... I've been attacked by bees... What a day! I'll be
waiting for you at Shade Tree Pier. Can you come talk?

View Mission Details {decision}

Having a band would make the party more lively. I need your
help. I'll be waiting for you in Gear Forest Village.

View Mission Details {decision}

Oh, no! Remember that secret base I told you about? Please
just come to the village!

View Mission Details {decision}

We're protectin' the peace of the forest! We're gonna start our
patrol from the Floating Island Plains!

View Mission Details {decision}

I've got a big favor to ask you. Could you stop by the shop when
you're in Central Town?

View Mission Details {decision}

My precious hammer is in trouble... My hammer is my life!
Come to the shop in Central Town. I'm begging you!

View Mission Details {decision}

I can't get a Parrotmon plume because the Titans are in the way!
Maybe I should go downtown and rethink the plan.

View Mission Details {decision}

Hmm... I still don't get it... I wanna talk about it some more, so
come to Rebellion Village.

View Mission Details {decision}

This feeling... I have to do something about it. Come meet me in
Rebellion Village.

View Mission Details {decision}

I want to go on a trip with Blimpmon. I can't stay in Central
Town forever!

View Mission Details {decision}

I can't go on like this...! I think I need your advice. I'll be waiting
