View Mission Details {decision}

I obtained a part from a most excellent action figure, and I've
got some questions about it. Come see me in the Factorial Core.

View Mission Details {decision}

Can you stop by the VIP room? I need to ask you a favor. It
shouldn't be a bad deal for you, either.

View Mission Details {decision}

The helpers I brought are in the Paradise Colosseum. You
should go see them and remind them of their role.

View Mission Details {decision}

We were running away from something scary, but my friend
didn't make it! I'm in Central Town. Please help!

View Mission Details {decision}

I managed to arrive at Central Tower on time... but everyone
in this world is so strong that I'm feeling a bit unsure of myself.

View Mission Details {decision}

I'll defeat the immortal steed of the Dark Garden, and in so
doing reclaim my confidence as a knight!

View Mission Details {decision}

Something strange is going on in Lord Plutomon's castle, but
I'm too scared to investigate... Someone, please help!

View Mission Details {decision}

Hey, come to Central Tower! I wanna show you all the Royal
Knights gathered here.

View Mission Details {decision}

I, Gallantmon, came to Factorial Town to fix my equipment,
but I did not expect to be stopped here... Hmm.

View Mission Details {decision}

I'm with WereGarurumon in the sanctuary of the Gear Forest.
I wonder why he hates humans so much...

View Mission Details {decision}

I have come all this way to Factorial Town, but I cannot get my
armor fixed. I need your help!

View Mission Details {decision}

I came to the Abyss Sanctuary to repair my armor, but how do
