View Mission Details {decision}

To think that not a single one of them could notice me... This
is a first. And here I have come all this way to Central Tower!

View Mission Details {decision}

I was just relaxing in the Shaded Woods, and then this really
strong-looking guy showed up!

View Mission Details {decision}

Ugh, how boring. Where the heck has Jesmon wandered off
to? Didn't I say to meet at the Paradise Colosseum?

View Mission Details {decision}

I am in line at Yaro-kei Ramen in Akihabara, but no matter
what I say, I always end up with the wrong order....

View Mission Details {decision}

A friend of mine seems to be involved in some kind of trouble.
I need you to come to the back alleys of Akihabara.

View Mission Details {decision}

We've recovered most of our strength. Head on over to
Central Tower as soon as you can. We'll be waiting for you!

View Mission Details {decision}

I heard a cosplayer went missing in Shinjuku Park. I wanna
investigate, so let's meet up at the Waterfall Plaza.

View Mission Details {decision}

There are a few Digimon that are really afraid of humans. I'll go
to your house in Central Town to tell you all about it.

View Mission Details {decision}

Can you come here quick? I got a super creepy Digiline.
Let's meet up at Vision Square in Higashi-Shinjuku!

View Mission Details {decision}

I came all the way to Abyss Beach and no one is here...
I wanna have fun with everyone in the ocean.

View Mission Details {decision}

There's something I want to do and I need your help. I'll be
waiting for you in downtown Central Town.

View Mission Details {decision}

This strange letter arrived at Inori's pop's office and I'm not
sure what to do. Anyone got any advice?

View Mission Details {decision}

What does "the Twentiest" even mean...? I'm so lost right now,
so I'm just standing in a back alley in Shinjuku...

View Mission Details {decision}

Sure, I've gotten stronger. But now that Big Bro is... What
should we do with the Paradise Colosseum?

View Mission Details {decision}

The time has come to see which is the true Card King. I await
