View Mission Details {decision}

I need to talk to you. I'll be waiting for you in a back alley of
Akihabara.

View Mission Details {decision}

I need to tell you about something that's been bothering me... I
can only share it with you. I'll be waiting at my house downtown!

View Mission Details {decision}

I got a tip about a missing person case. Could you come by
the office and give me a hand? 

View Mission Details {decision}

There's someone I want you to meet. We're meeting at the
office, so I want you to come, too.

View Mission Details {decision}

I found a picture of me back in high school. Come join me for
a reminiscing sesh! I'll be waiting for you at the office.

View Mission Details {decision}

I have a somewhat troublesome matter on my hands. I would
like you to stop by the tavern when you are in Central Town.

View Mission Details {decision}

The three hosts have something they'd like to convey to you.
Please come to the VIP room of the In-Between Theater.

View Mission Details {decision}

The fog is so bad, I can't get any deeper into the forest. I got
scared and came back to the village...

View Mission Details {decision}

I've found another occurrence of abnormal space. I'd like you
to investigate. I'll be waiting at the In-Between Theater.

View Mission Details {decision}

I've picked up a reading unlike anything I've ever seen before.
Come to the In-Between Theater.

View Mission Details {decision}

Lately I've been having these weird dreams... But they're super
real, like I'm actually there. This could be my next big scoop!

View Mission Details {decision}

A problem concerning the natural laws of the world has arisen.
I'd like you to investigate it.

View Mission Details {decision}

There's something I'd like you to investigate. Someone is
distorting the very precepts of our world.

View Mission Details {decision}

There's something I'd like you to investigate. Someone is
altering the flow of time itself.

View Mission Details {decision}
